We have a as spelt out the functional and non fuctional requirement our softwae will need to function.

Fuctional Requirements:With the assumption tahat we already have the data.
*Loading the data onto an array in the system.
*Generating a plot from the loaded data(pie-chart,bar,time-series).
*Further generates a brief statistical interpretation of the plot.

Use Case:
A user should be able to quer to have a short forcast report depicting some statistics on the data.

Non-Functional Requirements:
*Interaction with the central system of the hospitals to get information on the related disease within a specific time frame.


